1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,729
One moment she held the poisoned wine,
forcing me to thank her for my own death.
The next, she turns and runs.

2
00:00:05,329 --> 00:00:09,089
Those eyes... you shouldn't have eyes like
that! Guards — help —

3
00:00:09,489 --> 00:00:15,831
She knows it better than anyone: a deposed
concubine meant to die by poison should
never open eyes like these.

4
00:00:16,231 --> 00:00:25,235
I'd taken half a step and was already
behind her. So fast it stunned even me —
this isn't my skill; a dark-gold heat is
moving my body.

5
00:00:25,635 --> 00:00:32,593
My palm lands on her back. The feel is
wrong — not flesh, but cold tanned hide,
covered in fine scales.

6
00:00:32,993 --> 00:00:34,594
Just as I thought. You're not human.

7
00:00:35,194 --> 00:00:37,287
You little wretch! You've ruined
everything —

8
00:00:37,687 --> 00:00:39,261
Demon body detected. Refine it?

9
00:00:39,661 --> 00:00:39,969
Refine.

10
00:00:40,669 --> 00:00:52,049
She shrieks, her body withering before my
eyes, dissolving into a roiling cloud of
black smoke — drawn inch by inch into my
palm.

11
00:00:52,449 --> 00:00:59,199
No blood. Only a pool of bubbling, foul
liquid, and an empty dark-blue robe
collapsed on the floor.

12
00:00:59,599 --> 00:01:01,417
Demon devoured, power seized. Gained:
false human skin — stealth.

13
00:01:02,117 --> 00:01:10,575
Now I understand. This is no empty game of
leveling up. It's eating. Devour a demon,
take all it has — eat one, grow one
measure stronger, gain one art.

14
00:01:11,175 --> 00:01:17,961
But the price comes at once. The heat
suddenly ebbs away, my whole body drained
hollow, my vision going black.

15
00:01:18,361 --> 00:01:26,237
I catch the wooden couch to keep from
falling, cold sweat on my brow. Power
isn't free. One feeding — only one — at a
time.

16
00:01:26,637 --> 00:01:35,326
The gold light withdraws from my eyes, my
phoenix eyes turning ordinary black again.
I look down at the foul pool still
bubbling on the floor.

17
00:01:35,726 --> 00:01:37,263
Madam Liu... was a demon.

18
00:01:37,663 --> 00:01:41,801
Then this cold palace that swallows people
whole — how many more lie hidden here?
